reviewText: Has some good Tina Russel hard vintage, but NOT much else. Thanks for the good advice not to bother. Video was not related to the DVD cover image, and the video time was too short.
Was looking for candy barr vintage films. This dvd has nothing on candy barr,just her photo and name on the cover. this dvd is a complete fraud, not worth the money. I was ripprd off.

Don't buy this DVD if you are looking for Rene Bond or Candy Barr.  The only place you will see them is on the cover.  The loops on this DVD feature Tari Hall and are mediocre at best.  Even at these low prices this is a waste of money.  Be warned!
